Output demo.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15

Type "gh wut --help"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "gh wut ctx -R maxbeizer/claudia"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "gh wut story -R maxbeizer/claudia 67"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
